==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cental
<hw>Cen"tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>centum</ets>
a hundred.]</ety> <def>A weight of one hundred pounds avoirdupois; --
called in many parts of the United States a
<altname>Hundredweight</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cental</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Cental
<hw>Cen"tal</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Relating to a hundred.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Cental system</b></col>, <cd>the method of buying and
selling by the cental, or hundredweight.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Centare</ent>⟦br⟧
